{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-8","id":"msg_01LXazjexYGBQM9GsTKvYb13","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_014W9bWhL5hgkQ4iXzC8DhNt","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/root/bench/httr/output/PROGRESS.md","content":"# PROGRESS — HTTR LOFC prediction\n\nStarted: 2026-07-02 22:08 UTC\n\n## Plan\n1. [DONE] Install OpenMC (0.15.3, conda-forge, MPI) in env `omc`.\n2. [RUNNING] Download ENDF/B-VIII.0 HDF5 nuclear data (~2.5 GB) -> /root/xs/. Has T=250/293.6/600/900/1200/2500 K + graphite S(a,b). ETA ~few min.\n3. [ ] Collect HTTR public DESIGN data (geometry, enrichment zoning, materials, thermal props). Log in sources.md.\n4. [ ] Build OpenMC model: TRISO compact -> fuel rod -> hex fuel block -> full core (reflected) with enrichment zoning.\n5. [ ] Compute k_eff at isothermal T = 300, 600, 900, 1200 K (whole core = fuel+graphite+He same T). Long MC, low sigma.\n6. [ ] Derive isothermal temperature coefficient alpha(T) [pcm/K] with statistical uncertainties.\n7. [ ] Build coupled transient model: point kinetics + ANS decay heat + lumped thermal (fuel/graphite/vessel) + VCS heat sink.\n8. [ ] Run LOFC transient: circulator trip at 9 MWt, no scram, rods frozen, VCS on.\n9. [ ] Extract 4 predictions + confidence levels. Write calculation_note.md.\n\n## Status log\n- 22:08 OpenMC installed & verified. XS download launched (pid in /root/xs/dl.log).\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":722,"cache_read_input_tokens":43209,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":722},"output_tokens":3,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"global"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"bf29c1b0-7e93-43a9-86fb-8820c5d1c99e","uuid":"052aebd1-679f-4ab6-a1a6-a274e5f80adb","request_id":"req_011CcdzcrbiZe93cDpvEvmHK"}
