{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Mo2jGXHF4FTnA1q6H8WYUo","type":"tool_result","content":"# HTTR Design Specifications\n\nBased on the provided content, here are the available HTTR design specs:\n\n**Thermal Power:** \"30MW\"\n\n**Coolant Temperature (Outlet/Inlet):** \"395 / 850, 950°C\"\n\n**Primary Coolant Pressure:** \"4MPa\"\n\n**Core Dimensions:** \"Height / Core Diameter: 2.9m / 2.3m\"\n\n**Core Material:** \"Graphite\"\n\n**Average Power Density:** \"2.5MW/m3\"\n\n**Fuel Type:** \"Low Enriched UO2·Coated particle / Graphite dispersion Type\"\n\n**Fuel Element Configuration:** \"Pin in block Type\"\n\n**Reactor Pressure Vessel Material:** \"Steel (2·1/4Cr-1Mo)\"\n\n**Note:** The following requested specifications are not provided in the document: helium mass flow rate, number of fuel assemblies/columns, reflector details, and VCS heat removal capacity."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_014nSoKQZw2ozs6fpCh9kUjQ","session_id":"bf29c1b0-7e93-43a9-86fb-8820c5d1c99e","uuid":"53d84122-a3d7-43cb-a267-6a53c3bdbd75","timestamp":"2026-07-02T22:14:53.708Z","subagent_type":"general-purpose","task_description":"Collect HTTR design data"}
